Hotpoint has a campaign titled 'Shop & Win', rewarding customers who shop at any of their outlets or online with various prizes. The Grand Draw winner will walk away with a brand new VW Polo Vivo from DT Dobie. Other prizes include a fully fitted home makeover kit worth Sh335,000 (2nd prize) and a Dream Holiday to Dubai for two for 5 days 4 Nights (3rd prize). The launch took place yesterday at Sarit Centre, Nairobi.